## VoteModule.execute() method

Execute Proposal

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript

```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  proposalId | string | The proposal id to execute. |

<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;void&gt;

## Remarks

Execute the related transactions for a proposal if the proposal succeeded.
